Class Game

  • java.lang.Object
    • Game
  • public class Game
extends Object
    This class is the main class of the "College of Raritan" application. "College of Raritan" is a very simple, text based adventure game. Users can walk around some scenery. Pick up and drop items, eat some items, use a personal transporter. To play this game, create an instance of the class GameMain. This class creates and initialises all the others: it creates all rooms, items, player, and doors, creates the parser and starts the game. It also evaluates and executes the commands that the parser returns.
